{"title":"Adidas Velocade Indoor Trainer Shoes Power Your Clipless Workout & Walk Off-the-Bike","link":"https://bikerumor.com/adidas-velocade-indoor-trainer-shoes-power-your-clipless-workout-walk-off-the-bike/","date":1706553929000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_speed-blur.jpg\" alt=\"Adidas Velocade walkable mesh indoor cycling shoes, pedaling blur\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_speed-blur.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_speed-blur-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_speed-blur-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_speed-blur-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_speed-blur-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_speed-blur-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_speed-blur-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>These new Adidas Velocade indoor cycling shoes transition off the bike, so you can go with the rest of your life without swapping shoes right after your workout. Mixing up sneaker and sandal styling, Adidas calls the Velocade a performance hybrid indoor cycling shoe that doesn’t have to get stuck only on the stationary bike. Why not work out in a shoe you can wear around the house, around the office, or even around town to get a post-workout coffee…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Adidas Velocade walkable mesh indoor cycling shoes</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1500\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_front-while-riding.jpg\" alt=\"Adidas Velocade walkable mesh indoor cycling shoes, front on the trainer\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_front-while-riding.jpg 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_front-while-riding-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_front-while-riding-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_front-while-riding-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_front-while-riding-768x768.jpg 768w\" /><figcaption>(Photos/Adidas)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We’re always quite curious to see new cycling shoes from Adidas. With a storied cycling history on the biggest road racing stage, the off-road power of the Five Ten legacy in-house, plus more and more gravel &amp; lifestyle cycling options, the athletic shoe &amp; sportswear behemoth is really dipping their toe back in the cycling market.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_German-socks-and-sandals.jpg\" alt=\"Adidas Velocade walkable mesh indoor cycling shoes, German socks &amp; sandals\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_German-socks-and-sandals.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_German-socks-and-sandals-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_German-socks-and-sandals-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_German-socks-and-sandals-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_German-socks-and-sandals-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_German-socks-and-sandals-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_German-socks-and-sandals-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Their latest shoe is this Adidas Velocade clipless indoor trainer shoe. This bright green variation looks almost like the rider is wearing sandals over white socks. But, the all-black or white shoes look much more like a normal sneaker. Easily something you could wear off the bike, assuming you don’t click when you walk.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_all-black.jpg\" alt=\"Adidas Velocade walkable mesh indoor cycling shoes, simple black side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_all-black.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_all-black-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_all-black-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_all-black-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_all-black-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_all-black-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_all-black-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Adidas Velocade walkable mesh indoor cycling shoes, simple black side\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Adidas Velocade walkable mesh indoor cycling shoes, simple black side\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>“Velocade is our answer to two of the most common barriers athletes face when trying to fit in a high-quality workout: time and equipment. The ‘hidden’ two-bolt cleat means no more awkward and noisy walks between the changing room, bike and smoothie bar and no waiting to change footwear. Whether it’s high intensity workouts in the gym or your home, commuting, or going on adventures in new places, we are passionate about helping more people to clip in to the power of cycling. With Velocade we have focused on delivering this for the indoor cycling enthusiast – helping them to maximise not just their workouts but how they move through their whole routine.”</p>\n<cite><em>– Ben Herath, VP Design, adidas Specialist Sports</em></cite></blockquote>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech details</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1500\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_stretching-with-SPD-cleat.jpg\" alt=\"Adidas Velocade walkable mesh indoor cycling shoes, strechting with SPD cleat\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_stretching-with-SPD-cleat.jpg 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_stretching-with-SPD-cleat-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_stretching-with-SPD-cleat-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_stretching-with-SPD-cleat-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_stretching-with-SPD-cleat-768x768.jpg 768w\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Adidas specifically created the Velocade for versatility – on- and off the bike – much like their <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=velosamba\" target=\"_blank\">Velosamba</a>. But the Velocade leans more towards the performance side of the equation. With a 2/3-length fiber-reinforced nylon midsole plate for pedaling efficiency on 2-bolt MTB cleats. Those most often used on stationary bikes at the gym. Outside of that though, the rest of the shoe is flexible for comfortable walkability, especially the heel.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_non-marking-SPD-sole-detail.jpg\" alt=\"Adidas Velocade walkable mesh indoor cycling shoes, sole detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_non-marking-SPD-sole-detail.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_non-marking-SPD-sole-detail-297x165.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_non-marking-SPD-sole-detail-800x444.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_non-marking-SPD-sole-detail-120x67.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_non-marking-SPD-sole-detail-768x427.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_non-marking-SPD-sole-detail-1536x853.jpg 1536w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Adidas Velocade walkable mesh indoor cycling shoes, sole detail\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Adidas Velocade walkable mesh indoor cycling shoes, sole detail\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The trick to crossing over, the shoes feature a long, deep cleat pocket surrounded by a street shoe tread. That’s something I’ve seen done well, or not so well. Not having ridden these (or the Velosambas), I can only rely on anecdotes that say Adidas did a good job of keeping at least SPD cleats from hitting the ground as you walk.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_single-velcro-strap.jpg\" alt=\"Adidas Velocade walkable mesh indoor cycling shoes, velcro straop\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_single-velcro-strap.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_single-velcro-strap-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_single-velcro-strap-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_single-velcro-strap-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_single-velcro-strap-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_single-velcro-strap-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_single-velcro-strap-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Reasonably light at 230g (<em>claimed</em>) per shoe. The Velocade features a light-vented mesh ‘sock’ upper with one big strap that zig-zags across the top. And there’s just a single velcro patch at the end to adjust fit.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1350\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_side.jpg\" alt=\"Adidas Velocade walkable mesh indoor cycling shoes, side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_side.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_side-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_side-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_side-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_side-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_side-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Adidas Velocade – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"2500\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_colors.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Adidas Velocade walkable mesh indoor cycling shoes, colors\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_colors.jpg 2500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_colors-297x119.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_colors-800x320.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_colors-120x48.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_colors-768x307.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_colors-1536x614.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Adidas-Velocade-walkable-mesh-indoor-cycling-shoes_colors-2048x819.jpg 2048w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"2024 Adidas Velocade walkable mesh indoor cycling shoes, colors\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"2024 Adidas Velocade walkable mesh indoor cycling shoes, colors\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Adidas Velocade shoes sell for $130 / 150€, and are available now in Crystal Jade white &amp; neon green, Carbon black, and Grey One white &amp; silver. They come in unisex US half-sizing from US M5-11/W6-12. Find them in a select number of retailers, or direct from Adidas in your own country.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.adidas.com/us/cycling-shoes\" target=\"_blank\">adidas.com/US/cycling-shoes </a></em>or <em><a href=\"https://www.adidas.de/radfahren\" target=\"_blank\">adidas.de/radfahren</a></em>, for example</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/adidas-velocade-indoor-trainer-shoes-power-your-clipless-workout-walk-off-the-bike/\">Adidas Velocade Indoor Trainer Shoes Power Your Clipless Workout &amp; Walk Off-the-Bike</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"4032ed61ea2ff1fb3ccb584d37d0e31540a02b6dca0acea3bc42a0d9969ddb4c","category":"Cycling"}